nixpkgs / jetbrains.rider - JetBrains Rider is a new .NET IDE based on the IntelliJ platform and ReSharper. Rider supports .NET Core, .NET Framework and Mono based projects. This lets you develop a wide array of applications including .NET desktop apps, services and libraries, Unity games, ASP.NET and ASP.NET Core web applications.

Homepage - https://www.jetbrains.com/rider/

Maintainers - Vasiliy Solovey
